 false}, {"url_token": "li-xiao-ran-39", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "500311027", "reply_comment_id": "457324133", "reply_root_comment_id": "457324133", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "大晚上在路上低速晃也真的很讨厌", "like_count": 13, "author_name": "李小染", "author_id": "1e7c457b61a44e8dcae1a5c7f032b639", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wxf364a7a969b37c7a", "headline": "为中华民族的崛起而奋斗终生", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "496223320", "reply_comment_id": "457324133", "reply_root_comment_id": "457324133", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "个人意见要合理控制速度。如果过慢别人为了超车酿成事故怎么办？", "like_count": 13, "author_name": "Skyler", "author_id": "2e18e1d9d758981c6c34d50f5fc8216e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ri-yang-de-ha-li-fa", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "540919589", "reply_comment_id": "457324133", "reply_root_comment_id": "457324133", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "慢可以，请老老实实在最右侧爬，不要影响别人好吗？尤其是封闭式道路，前面毛都没有还在最左侧爬，这会暴露智商的。", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "羊骑士", "author_id": "dcc40baac7a755b4fa6ad29c71fd7a77", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ri-yang-de-ha-li-fa", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "661400691", "reply_comment_id": "661385964", "reply_root_comment_id": "457324133", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "如果是停了一大堆车的小路，开多慢我都没意见，没准我比他们还慢；普通城市道路如果存在大量盲区跟交汇路口的，就算我这样喜欢开快车的，三四十基本已经是极限了。但是，如果是视野良好的封闭式道路，限速60甚至80的还开30+，不好意思，请走最右侧。<br>另外，在我看来，左快右慢仅限于封闭式道路（出口全在右侧的那种），普通道路要按照行进方向选择车道，这种条件下我也不会要求慢车靠右。", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "羊骑士", "author_id": "dcc40baac7a755b4fa6ad29c71fd7a77", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "li-li-33-25-76", "headline": "结构的/上班的/行走的", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637768060", "reply_comment_id": "529871421", "reply_root_comment_id": "457324133", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "前几天去高铁站送老公，居然发现快车道最里侧有遛狗的老头老太太", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "susu88", "author_id": "a52155a1fa159f7a3da81a953ac180bc", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "peng-wen-jun-40-69", "headline": "心宽体胖", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1194580076", "reply_comment_id": "457324133", "reply_root_comment_id": "457324133", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "也没必要一只三四十，看路况和附近情况，路过村庄之类的减速时刻准备踩刹车，过人行道等等提前减速，其他时间正常开", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "天堂在左", "author_id": "3feddb3d62d9c79c16d7b68a906aed72", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "xiao-ming-36-64", "headline": "你好谢谢再见", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "457979188", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "457979188", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>单位开通勤大巴的老司机，驾龄30年，市区驾驶大巴超车自如，秒杀大部分私家车。称从来不敢在马路牙以下区域走路或骑车，从来不敢闯红灯过马路。害怕电动车。</p>", "like_count": 66, "author_name": "小明", "author_id": "27bc20354994f5648b51313598615df4", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "shan-chuan-bi-bo", "headline": "荒途长跋涉", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "457403927", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "457403927", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "是的！！！！开车的时候大老远看到个人都怕的不行  然而没学车前我都是闭着眼过马路 我太可怕了", "like_count": 46, "author_name": "山川碧波", "author_id": "939b3e5a8cab526b40cd5c3cf02cb40f", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "sky-46-91", "headline": "谨言慎行", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "457496276", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "457496276", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "说得太对了，去年学车之前一直都是一辆小电动大街小巷窜来窜去，后来自己考驾照科目三真正上路了之后真心感叹自己命大:-D", "like_count": 23, "author_name": "是阿星呀", "author_id": "3dd1ad8c0d99b63bcc7275cbf97cfebf", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "ku-qi-de-dao-feng", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "494742698", "reply_comment_id": "457496276", "reply_root_comment_id": "457496276", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "电动车又不一样，电动车就算不开灯侧面也有反光板。虽然很小，但是不亚于图示的反光带。当然那种不开灯，反光板也掉了的，就……", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "正月十九", "author_id": "d9296f451f0558f913987a57320b57ca", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "jiang-min-86-9", "headline": "普通的ACG爱好者", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "457445196", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "457445196", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "盲区很多，坐上车就能拿上知道一部分盲区，学过驾驶就能知道剩下的盲区", "like_count": 19, "author_name": "南極", "author_id": "f283da51af14cfe6c4cee6a44eb7e09d", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "mrtian-95", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "490151954", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "490151954", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "说点别的，我个人是比较提倡安全驾驶的，比较反对暴力驾驶。之前拉领导外出办事，开环岛路限速50（没摄像头），都是连续过弯的山路。我就保持50左右的时速行驶，结果领导不乐意了，说太慢，叫我靠边停车，他来开。一上车就开始冲到80，一路上各种表演超速，违规变道超车等等。<br>我胆子不小，但我还是怕死的。山路本来就小，视野也差。如果违规超速变道，刚好拐弯处迎面来一辆车，就GG了<br>老司机技术好不假，但没必要各种违规炫技，快也就快那么一时半会，运气不好就快别人几十年了，有意思吗？遵守交通规则和老老实实各行其道就那么难吗？<br>领导，你不怕死我还想多活几年……", "like_count": 14, "author_name": "Mr田", "author_id": "8522e6d50889fe90cbd62dedbca1eee4", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "pandorabiol", "headline": "生化，组织学", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "461438648", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "461438648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "真是这样，我有时候晚上会看见一身黑色的人横穿马路，真的是非常非常近了我才看到，活活吓死，真心建议晚上不要一身黑", "like_count": 12, "author_name": "潘多拉神殿", "author_id": "f3ed64bfb4481f3741cb6e117c3057a5", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "ye-ma-97-43", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "464710678", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_com